<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Schema: styled_text_mim
<express_ref linkend="styled_text:mim:Text_representation_mim.registered_font_constraint"/>
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Text_representation_mim.registered_font_constraint">
The <b>registered_font_constraint</b> rule constrains all <express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.externally_defined_text_font"/>
instances to have an assigned font registration document.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Text_representation_mim.registered_font_constraint.wr:WR1">
Each instance of <express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.externally_defined_text_font"/>
shall be referenced as a member of <express_ref linkend="Document_assignment:mim:Document_assignment_mim.applied_document_reference.items"/>
of at least one <express_ref linkend="Document_assignment:mim:Document_assignment_mim.applied_document_reference"/>, that
has <express_ref linkend="document_schema:ir_express:document_schema.document_type.product_data_type"/> of
<express_ref linkend="document_schema:ir_express:document_schema.document.kind"/> of
<express_ref linkend="management_resources_schema:ir_express:management_resources_schema.document_reference.assigned_document"/>
set to 'font registration document'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Schema: styled_text_mim
<express_ref linkend="styled_text:mim:Text_representation_mim.registered_font_unique_constraint"/>
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Text_representation_mim.registered_font_unique_constraint">
The <b>registered_font_unique_constraint</b> requires the combination of <express_ref linkend="external_reference_schema:ir_express:external_reference_schema.externally_defined_item.item_id"/>
and font registration document to be unique
in the population of <express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.externally_defined_text_font">externally_defined_text_fonts</express_ref>.
</ext_description>

<ext_description linkend="Text_representation_mim.registered_font_unique_constraint.wr:WR1">
There shall not be two or more <express_ref linkend="presentation_resource_schema:ir_express:presentation_resource_schema.externally_defined_text_font">externally_defined_text_fonts</express_ref>
that have same <express_ref linkend="external_reference_schema:ir_express:external_reference_schema.externally_defined_item.item_id"/> and
are refered as members of <express_ref linkend="Document_assignment:mim:Document_assignment_mim.applied_document_reference.items"/>
by <express_ref linkend="Document_assignment:mim:Document_assignment_mim.applied_document_reference">applied_document_references</express_ref>
that refer same <express_ref linkend="document_schema:ir_express:document_schema.document"/>, having
<express_ref linkend="document_schema:ir_express:document_schema.document_type.product_data_type"/> of
<express_ref linkend="document_schema:ir_express:document_schema.document.kind"/> set to 'font registration document',
as <express_ref linkend="management_resources_schema:ir_express:management_resources_schema.document_reference.assigned_document"/>.
</ext_description>
